gomodel:SYNGO_4185  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: - Postembedding immunogold EM of adult rat cerebral cortex was performed using 254.2 anti-liprin2-antibody.\n\n- Fig. 5D EM images show the expression of gold particles associated with synaptic vesicles.. Experimental description: Rat hippocampal neuron cultures were prepared from hippocampi dissected from E18 rat embryos as described (Goslin and Banker, 1991)." ;
